Expand your thinking
Speed up drafts
Automate repetitive mental work

You still own the decisions.

You are the thought leader
AI is the thought partner

Ask yourself: “How can AI help me do this?”

#AILeadership #KnowledgeWork #FutureOfWork

Stop treating AI like a crystal ball.
Start treating it like an eager, smart junior associate.

Vague asks = vague results

Set context, define goals, share examples.  That’s where the magic happens.

キャラメルやビスケットの菓子、ココアやケーキミックスの食品などを製造・販売する森永製菓株式会社が制定。
